Test 1: "Explain codetalk session type"
  Result: PASS | 2 turns | 1 codetalk child | $0.0476 | stdout: 21 lines ✓
  Tools: start_session(1), get_session_progress(1)

Test 2: "Trace full request lifecycle"
  Result: PASS | 2 turns | 1 codetalk child | $0.0747 | stdout: 75 lines ✓
  Tools: start_session(1), get_session_progress(1)

